{
  "text": "Referring to the normal condition of the SST in eastern Pacific Ocean which is commonly higher than the SST in western Indian Ocean [CITATION_1] , the value of SST in the western Pacific Ocean were subtracted by SST in the eastern Indian Ocean for knowing the differences between those both ocean when the ENSO occurred. A simple formulation to calculate the SST difference is as follows:",
